title: WHY YOU'RE STUCK IN LIFE....
description:
Hey Rehabbers,
Today's podcast will help you move from the things that make you powerless to the things that create power in our life. I spend time today helping you STOP THE FLOW that's leading you to pain, and help you create a flow that leads you to your greatness. I know today's episode will speak to your soul!
How you can help me? 
Just share this episode on your social media and tag me, or simply just text the link to a friend that you think could use these words.

Come Protect Your Peace with me at THE PROTECT YOUR PEACE MASTERMIND/RETREAT 
Go to www.rehabuniversity.com to find more information.
